data.description: Located on the northwest side of Odessa you have yourself a 3 bed 2 bath family home. A little over 5 minutes to i70 making for fast travel to work or running errands. Walk in the front door and be greeted by a split level entry. Go upstairs to find the cozy living room with a fireplace and vaulted ceiling. This house also features a finished basement with a walk out garage! Walking out the back door, you have a large fenced in backyard that would be perfect for entertaining and a shed for all of your outside storage items. Bring your family and your own personal touch.
